title: Healthenut Cafe and Juice Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, All Raw
description: Organic live food cafe and juice bar offering daily specials and a menu of raw food and dessert that are free of wheat, dairy, processed refined sugar, and animal products. Its retail area sells whole organic supplements plus packaged raw crackers and other goodies. The one is a nutritionist who hosts raw food preparation classes.
